      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GARY INDIANA (2) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a 2.5 lengths win at this track in a handy 23.08. Has a low draw and has a good record over this journey. Ideally placed to take this out. DOLLAR ROLEX (8) has a strong record here with two wins and a minor from three starts. Hit the frame latest (17.92) when second at Taree Super Track in a Grade 5. Can hit the frame with the right run. CHUTZPAH (1) turned in a modest effort most recently when seventh at Gosford over 388m behind KILCOY TIGER (23.25) in a Grade 5. Placed at his previous run. Has the ability to give this a shake. CANYA PLEASE (6) collected a minor prize last start and must be considered.",
